<p>Especially for the <strong>Indian climate and lifestyle</strong>, maintaining healthy hair and skin requires specialized care that addresses local environmental factors, diet, and genetics.</p>

<h2>White Hair Spreading Kyun Hoti Hai? — Melanocyte Exhaustion Pattern</h2>
        <p>Samajhne ke liye pehle ye jaanein of baalon ko color kaifrom milta hai. Har hair follicle mein <strong>melanocytes</strong> happen — ye cells melanin pigment produce karte hain jo baalon ko kaala, brown ya dark color deta hai. Jab ye melanocytes kaam karna band kar dete hain ya mar jaate hain, toh hair white nikal aata hai.</p>

        <p>Ab ye process ek pattern mein hota hai — ifrom <strong>melanocyte exhaustion pattern</strong> kehte hain. Pehle kuch follicles mein melanocytes weaken happen, phir dheere-dheere neighboring follicles also affect happen. Ye koi infection nahi hai jo fail raha — balof ye ek gradual depletion hai jo body mein chal rahi hai.</p>

        <p>Ek important baat — melanocyte stem cells ek baar khatam ho jaayein toh wapas nahi aate. Isliye <strong>early intervention</strong> sabfrom critical hai. Jitna jaldi aap action loge, utne zyada active melanocytes bachayenge.</p>

        
