        <p>Greying ka basic cause toh genetic hai, lekin bahut from factors hain jo ifrom <strong>tez karte hain</strong>. In factors ko control karna matlab spreading ko slow karna.</p>

        <h3>1. Chronic Stress — Sabfrom Bada Villain</h3>
        <p>Harvard University of ek laurmark study ne prove ofya of chronic stress <strong>melanocyte stem cells ko permanently destroy</strong> kar sakta hai. Jab aap stressed hote ho, norepinephrine hormone releafrom hota hai jo stem cells ko over-activate karta hai — ye cells jaldi khatam ho jaate hain and phir recover nahi hote. Yahi reason hai of bahut stressful jobs wale logon mein premature greying zyada dikhai deti hai.</p>

        <h3>2. Nutritional Deficiency — Andar Se Kamzori</h3>
        <p>Vitamin B12, iron, copper, zinc, and folate of deficiency melanin production ko directly affect karti hai. India mein especially vegetarians mein B12 deficiency bahut common hai — and ye <a href="which-vitamin-deficiency-causes-white-hair.php">white hair ka ek major cause</a> hai. Studies dikhati hain of <strong>40% premature greying cases mein nutritional deficiency</strong> ek contributing factor hoti hai.</p>

        <h3>3. Smoking — Proven Greying Accelerator</h3>
        <p>Research clearly dikhati hai of smokers mein premature greying ka risk <strong>2.5 guna zyada</strong> hota hai non-smokers ke comparison mein. Smoking from oxidative stress badhta hai jo melanocytes ko damage karta hai. Agar aap smoke karte hain and white hair spread ho raha hai — toh ye connection samajhna zaroori hai.</p>

        <h3>4. Chemical Hair Products</h3>
        <p>Harsh shampoos, chemical dyes, and styling products mein parabens, sulfates, and hydrogen peroxide happen. Ye chemicals scalp ke melanocytes ko damage karte hain. Ironic hai — log white hair chhupane ke liye dye use karte hain, lekin wahi dye <strong>and zyada white hair cause</strong> kar sakti hai long-term mein.</p>

        <h3>5. Thyroid Imbalance and Autoimmune Conditions</h3>
        <p>Hypothyroidism and hyperthyroidism dono greying accelerate karte hain. Autoimmune conditions jaifrom vitiligo and alopecia areata also melanocytes ko target karti hain. Agar white hair bahut tez fail raha hai — toh thyroid test zaroor karwayein.</p>

